Package net.objectzoo.ebc.state

This package contains interfaces and classes that are use to implement different state holding mechanisms for EBCs.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    State<Value>
    This interface represents a state that can be hold by an EBC.
    StateFactory
    A StateFactory is used to create a new State instances.
    ValueFactory<Value>
    The ValueFactory is used to create the initial value for a State hold by an EBC.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicStateFactory
    A StateFactory implementation that creates BasicState instances.

Package net.objectzoo.ebc.state Description
